Invocation Name: birthday greetings
des:
Wish <your-friend-name>
This skill will address your friend by their name and deliver a lovely birthday quote along with funky birthday music. 


You can also ask the send your name as part of greeting by saying "Wish <your-friend-name> from <your-name>". 

Your friends will love this surprise
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
